data.description: Stunning country setting for this unique brick home. From the columned entrance, brick driveway and tiled courtyard, this home is a gem! Main floor offers 3 bedrooms 2.5 baths, formal living room with stone fireplace, den/library just off formal living room with a spiral staircase leading up to an office area. Family room with fireplace that leads to a roomy sunroom that looks out to brick patio and inground pool. Large eat-in kitchen with tons of cabinets and planning area, and formal dining room. Primary bedroom has private bath in addition to a large dressing/closet area (23' x 7'). 2nd bedroom has built in cabinetry and 3rd bedroom offers large coset. Basement has an additional family/living area with fireplace, 2nd kitchen and full bath. All this on a little over 1.5 acres! Don't miss this opportunity!
